Revision history for perl module Alien-IUP

0.703_1 2015-05-29
    -  IMPORTANT: switch to iup-3.14+im-3.9.1+cd-5.8.2

0.703 2015-02-08
    -  improved checking of OpenGL libraries (UNIX)

0.702 2015-02-06
    -  cygwin related patches

